<div class="kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id8_848d2a-a9 alignnone wp-block-kadence-rowlayout" id="fast-websites"><div class="kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-2-columns kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-inherit kt-mobile-layout-row kt-row-valign-middle kt-inner-column-height-full">

<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column8_feb954-06 img-appear-section3"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column8_654b67-0e"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col">
<h2 class="kt-adv-heading8_acef7c-f1 text-reveal1-title wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading8_acef7c-f1">Websites Built to Perform at Every Level</h2>



<h3 class="kt-adv-heading8_a83d31-87 text-reveal1-subtitle wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading8_a83d31-87">All-Green Performance by Design</h3>



<p class="kt-adv-heading8_450b1c-a5 scroll-up wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading8_450b1c-a5">We promise real performance, not empty numbers.<br>Every website we build is coded from scratch for speed, stability and long-term growth. No templates, no heavy builders – only clean structure that loads instantly and meets all Core Web Vitals standards.<br>Our builds consistently reach all-green Google PageSpeed scores. We optimise images, scripts and caching for every device and connection type. Your site will perform on mobile, desktop and future generative search systems that reward fast, well-structured content.<br>We test each website through Lighthouse, GTmetrix and independent audits to ensure lasting performance. This gives your business higher ranking potential, better user experience and stronger visibility in both Google Search and AI-driven results.<br>We stand behind every build. If it doesn’t pass our internal performance checks, it doesn’t launch.</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items8_1a9693-1e kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list">
<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-8_c09bb0-2c"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong>Speed</strong><br>Optimised code and server caching deliver instant load times that reduce bounce rate and improve ranking.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-8_936467-22"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong>Stability</strong><br>Each site is tested on multiple devices and browsers to guarantee reliable performance.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-8_51b8a4-9d"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong>Scalability</strong><br>Our framework adapts easily as your content, products or services grow without losing speed.</span></li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>

</div></div>

<div class="kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id8_9c0992-f5 alignnone wp-block-kadence-rowlayout"><div class="kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-2-columns kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-inherit kt-mobile-layout-row kt-row-valign-middle kt-inner-column-height-full">

<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column8_3908fe-8f"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col">
<h2 class="kt-adv-heading8_af790d-50 text-reveal1-title wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading8_af790d-50">Websites Ready for Every Marketing Channel</h2>



<h3 class="kt-adv-heading8_dfc05d-ae text-reveal1-subtitle wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading8_dfc05d-ae">Smart Web Design Built to Convert and Perform</h3>



<p class="kt-adv-heading8_507a7e-43 scroll-up wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading8_507a7e-43">We build websites ready to connect with your digital marketing from day one.<br>Every project is structured for PPC campaigns, Google Ads, Meta Ads, and social media tracking – all without slowing your site down.<br>Our builds include complete integration for analytics, events, and conversions. We prepare everything for accurate tracking across ads, search, and social platforms, so you can measure performance with confidence.<br>If you prefer a privacy-first setup, we can build your website completely cookieless. That means no banner, no unnecessary scripts, and full compliance with modern data regulations – while still giving you reliable performance data through privacy-safe methods.<br>Each website also includes social sharing optimisation. Titles, images and descriptions are preconfigured for Facebook, LinkedIn, and X (Twitter) to ensure your content looks perfect when shared.<br>We design for speed, visibility, and advertising success. Whether you plan to run PPC campaigns, social ads, or SEO campaigns, your website will already be ready for it.</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items8_c41ff3-92 kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list">
<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-8_32042f-73"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Ads Ready<br>Optimised for Google Ads, Meta Ads and remarketing from launch – no extra setup required.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-8_8aed21-87"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong>Analytics &amp; Tracking</strong><br>Conversion events, click tracking and form goals built into your structure.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-8_f4c1d2-16"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong>Cookieless Option</strong><br>We can create your site without third-party cookies – privacy-friendly, no banner needed, fully compliant.</span></li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>



